    "Welcome to CodeLume! To control the installation package size, we have built-in default dynamic wallpapers that have been automatically loaded. For more operations, please find the C-shaped icon in the status bar and click on it." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "欢迎使用码镜！为控制安装包体积，我们已内置默认动态壁纸并自动加载。更多操作请点击状态栏中的 C 形图标进行查看。"
          }
        }
      }
    }
